OST\'\\];[/PHP]/[New_Item.Type.Alias no_wrap /]/[New_Item.Alias no_wrap /]</a>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n	<!--  -->\n	<div class=\"Time\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n		Thanks!<br/>\n	</div>\n	\n	<!--  -->\n	<div class=\"Time\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n		[1 Site from Database no_wrap]\n			[Owner.Name no_wrap/] @ [Site.Name no_wrap/]<br/>\n			<a style=\"color:#41bde1;\" href=\"http://[PHP]return $_SERVER\\[\'HTTP_HOST\'\\];[/PHP]/[Owner.Alias no_wrap/]\">http://[PHP]return $_SERVER\\[\'HTTP_HOST\'\\];[/PHP]/[Owner.Alias no_wrap/]</a>\n		[/1]\n	</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background-color:#efefef;padding:20px;\">\n	Better helps creative & volunteer communities with a shared vision coordinate their free time to make enormous changes together.<br/>\n	<br/>\n	<a href=\"http://better.space/learn_more\" style=\"color:#FD6B03; font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\">LEARN MORE</a><br/>\n</div>','','',NULL,NULL,'Published');
